{"word":"H1880 - דֶּשֶׁן - deshen - deh'-shen - Ashes","slug":"H1880","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">דֶּשֶׁן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>deshen"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>deh'-shen"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Ashes"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DF; - deshen</b> - <i>deh'-shen</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1878\">H1878</a>; the <i>fat</i>; abstractly <i>fatness</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>abundance</i>; specifically the (fatty) <i>ashes</i> of sacrifices: - ashes, fatness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1878\">H1878</a>, <a href=\"#/H1879\">H1879</a>, <a href=\"#/H1881\">H1881</a>, <a href=\"#/H1885\">H1885</a>, <a href=\"#/H1886\">H1886</a>"}]}